<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>导购品类 on 短松江月</title><link>https://simons.qzz.io/tags/%E5%AF%BC%E8%B4%AD%E5%93%81%E7%B1%BB/</link><description>Recent content in 导购品类 on 短松江月</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Jan 2026 11:32:58 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://simons.qzz.io/tags/%E5%AF%BC%E8%B4%AD%E5%93%81%E7%B1%BB/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>品类三界之导购品类（上）</title><link>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/shopping_guide_categories_in_the_three_realms_part_1/</link><pubDate>Sun, 13 Apr 2025 07:59:06 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/shopping_guide_categories_in_the_three_realms_part_1/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;《品类三界之产品品类（上）》提到，由于商品的高度丰富，为了提高消费者的选择效率，导致导购分离，所以出现了导购品类。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;导购品类的历史很长，但一直是品类三界里面最弱的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在全球化的市场中，导购品类远比过去农业社会的复杂。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;导购品类聚焦于信息的处理，互联网正是这方面的利器，进而催生了各种综合导购和垂直导购。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>品类三界之产品品类（上）</title><link>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/product_categories_in_the_three_realms_of_categories_part_1/</link><pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 08:28:59 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/product_categories_in_the_three_realms_of_categories_part_1/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;人们对事物进行分类意味着人们对事物的某种认知有了进步。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;比如人们对生物的分类。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; 
